 係擋病毒個載體<br />\n你唔係以為病毒係一粒粒咁自己飛出黎下話, 咁全世界醫院可以摺埋"},{"pid":"0bedf60b6ed15466af234aaf98a2c26a3bdd23c5","tid":2283801,"uid":311412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:26:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[0:35] Myth 1: 口罩可以擋到病毒?<br />\n有個油牆工人戴左口罩 d 灰係10micron 大 corona virus 只有0.125 micron<br />\n咁大粒灰都可以自由穿過口罩 你認為你個口罩可以擋到Covid 嗎?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係口罩既作用從來唔係攞黎擋 airborne 既 COVID，而係用黎擋飛沫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/more/scientific-brief-sars-cov-2.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fcoronavirus%2F2019-ncov%2Fmore%2Fscientific-brief-sars-cov-2.html&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2BygWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=7e5c45fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/more/scientific-brief-sars-cov-2.html</a>"},{"pid":"06850d842dae6c25f3813ac908d2010663ee005a","tid":2283801,"uid":92307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:45:28.000Z","msg":"呢啲片如果武肺爆發初期拎出嚟都仲有討論空間嘅<br />\n但係之後台灣果邊已經有統計數字, 喺佢地全民口罩之後就連流感病毒感染數字都連帶顯住下跌<br />\n載口罩有冇用已經唔再係著眼點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c810b203e4c85ebb5cd9f779d0be7dd16780fde3","tid":2283801,"uid":196968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:47:51.000Z","msg":"不如我問你戴左口罩之後係咪少左傷風感冒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9443dab4e59480c218ba78e2ec0e6b5dbddf36a","tid":2283801,"uid":45529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:48:41.000Z","msg":"普通大學md, 專業唔係傳染病, 講嘢有參考價值咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b2dcecd21370f9cb7c9abbc09cfb100ea6e90d","tid":2283801,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"c810b203e4c85ebb5cd9f779d0be7dd16780fde3","tid":2283801,"uid":196968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:47:51.000Z","msg":"不如我問你戴左口罩之後係咪少左傷風感冒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:50:35.000Z","msg":"勤洗手而唔係口罩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d63c7a3bc70e606da9ae6245207aac0947d7c45","tid":2283801,"uid":28628,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e5d1c7ae7cc93a7bfd3f357f91285d6ca0e7994","tid":2283801,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"c46a061453daf2f7cb5b0cc65a04a2b9b42b108e","tid":2283801,"uid":28628,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T01:40:38.000Z","msg":"理論撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n實際上戴左口罩<br />\n係無爆得咁勁 <br />\n<br />\n同埋又係用all or nothing <br />\n既諗野方法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T01:44:15.000Z","msg":"又係單向思維撚<br />\n你有戴口罩 但同時好多人有勤洗手<br />\n有精神病人周圍噴消毒<br />\n宜家一個教授同你講 口罩personal use 係無用<br />\n你呢d 市井居民就質疑明明戴左有用<br />\n實際上有用嘅係大家勤洗手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:52:41.000Z","msg":"又係盲信權威撚<br />\n教授又點 教授就岩？<br />\n仲有佢只係Dr 唔係Prof.<br />\nDr title 我都有<br />\n仲有你叫個Surgeon 話戴口罩無用<br />\n有無big data support ?<br />\n你不如去問米啦好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明顯地有戴口罩係爆得無咁勁<br />\n(日本 香港 台灣 中國）<br />\n當然你勤洗手 係一定有用<br />\n但你點肯定戴口罩無用<br />\n如果你話口罩唔係full protection<br />\n我絕對同意 <br />\n連ccd都由叫人話戴口罩無用<br />\n改口叫人戴口罩 <br />\n好明顯條友係反口罩撚啦<br />\n有哂bias咁話口罩點無用<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41591-020-0843-2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41591-020-0843-2&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2BygWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=c2309ca1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41591-020-0843-2</a><br />\n拎去睇啦peer review journal嚟<br />\n唔係我呢d有PhD 既市井居民講架"},{"pid":"7488f4835ba946b81f8baf2b7321aeadd5440bb2","tid":2283801,"uid":196968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"99b2dcecd21370f9cb7c9abbc